     C                     PARM           PPORM   1        + OR -
     C                     PARM           PDAYS   4
     C                     PARM           PRDAT   8
     C                     PARM           PRTN    1
      *
     C                     MOVE PRDAT     WKYMD   80
      *
     C                     Z-ADDWKY       LBKANY
     C                     Z-ADDWKM       LBKANM
     C                     Z-ADDWKD       LBKAND
